1) Let's get it all out now. Correct any inaccuracies you see.
2) Always followup to c.o.msw.advocacy only: not to c.o.l.m.
3) Let's not post another word on the subject after 11:59 PM Sun August 22th.
   Come Monday morning let it wither on the vine.

Right now my Linux box can run MSDOS, X Windows, and VC based Unix all the
same time. I don't want NT, I don't need NT. I don't give a shit about NT.

Don't fall for this flame bait. Dump all the correct info in c.o.msw.advocacy.
They need the correct info. We don't. 

followups to c.o.msw.advocacy.

